            "title": "Objet: Wwake’s Art-Inspired Jewelry",
            "link": [
               "https://www.artnews.com/art-news/artists/wwake-art-inspired-jewelry-1234616106/"
            ],
            "creator": {
               "__cdata": "Anne Doran"
            },
            "pubDate": "Wed, 19 Jan 2022 21:01:45 +0000",
            "category": [
               {
