            "title": "Essentials: What Tapes to Use for Art and Conservation",
            "link": [
               "https://www.artnews.com/art-news/artists/the-right-tapes-for-art-and-conservation-1234616052/"
            ],
            "creator": {
               "__cdata": "Julia Travers"
            },
            "pubDate": "Wed, 19 Jan 2022 19:32:57 +0000",
            "category": [
