            "title": "MoCA Cleveland Picks Megan Lykins Reich to Fill Director Role Left Vacant Amid Controversy in 2020",
            "link": [
               "https://www.artnews.com/art-news/news/moca-cleveland-megan-lykins-reich-director-1234616047/"
            ],
            "creator": {
               "__cdata": "Alex Greenberger"
            },
            "pubDate": "Wed, 19 Jan 2022 16:16:33 +0000",
            "category": [
               {
                  "__cdata": "ARTnews"
